Jean Madar

Age : 56Public asset : 259,765,964 USDLinked companies :  Inter Parfums, Inc. -  Interparfums SA 





Summary 



Mr. Jean Madar is Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at Inter Parfums, Inc., Chief Executive Officer & Director at Inter Parfums Holding SA, and Executive Director at Interparfums.He is on the Board of Directors at Inter Parfums Holding SA and Interparfums.He received his undergraduate degree from ESSEC Business School.



