 Clients



Companies ▾




Interparfums


                                                                                     •  Paris, IF                                                                            

                                        Interparfums engages in the design, manufacture, and sale of cosmetics and fragrances. It distributes its products through the following brands: Balmain, Boucheron, Jimmy Choo, Karl Lagerfeld, Lanvin, Montblanc, Paul Smith, Repetto, S.T. Dupont, and Van Cleef & Arpels. The company was founded by Philippe Bénacin and Jean Madar in 1982 and is headquartered in Paris, France.
                                    




Evergreen International Holdings Ltd.


                                                                                     •  George Town, GT                                                                            

                                        Evergreen International Holdings Ltd. operates as an investment holding company, which engages in the manufacturing and trading of clothing and clothing accessories. The firm owns and manages two brands, V.E. DELURE and TESTANTIN. The V.E. DELURE brand offers business formal and casual menswear and accessories targeting men. The TESTANTIN brand offers contemporary and chic casual menswear and accessories targeting younger and more fashion conscious men. The company was founded on June 26, 2008 and is headquartered in Guangzhou, China.
                                    






